---
title: Roasted Tilapia with Garlic-Scallion Oil plus Creamy Chickpeas & Kale
description: Fresh scallions, zippy garlic, and bright lemon zest infuse their flavors into a finishing oil you'll drizzle over flaky roasted tilapia. Serve the fish over a savory mix of chickpeas and kale, swirled with tangy crème fraîche for a rich, creamy texture. Punch it up with a final squeeze of lemon juice, and get ready for one delicious fish dish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66e85c752d58b223b75b987a-3f4b1c74.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66e85c752d58b223b75b987a-en-US.pdf
course: main course
author: Michelle Doll Olson
time required: 25 minutes
nutrition:
